snippet: A dental examination confirmed that the body was that of Christopher J. Dorner, who the authorities believe killed four people, including two police officers.
abstract: Authorities say dental records confirm that body found inside burned-out cabin near Big Bear Lake, Calif, is that of Christopher J Dorner, who killed four people, including two police officers.
lead_paragraph: A dental examination confirmed that the body was that of Christopher J. Dorner, who the authorities believe killed four people, including two police officers.

headline.seo: Body in Cabin Is Identified as Christopher Dorner
headline.main: Body in Cabin Is Identified as Former Los Angeles Officer
